Privacy Policy for Ascii Weather

Effective Date: 2026-03-01

Ascii Weather ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our mobile application.

1. Information Collection and Use

Location Data We request access to your device's location solely to provide accurate local weather forecasts. This location data is processed locally on your device and sent directly to Apple's WeatherKit service to retrieve weather information. We do not store, track, or share your location history on our servers.

Personal Information We do not collect, store, or share any personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, email address, or phone number.

2. Third-Party Services

Apple WeatherKit Our app uses Apple's WeatherKit to provide weather data. Your location data is shared with Apple to fetch this information. Apple's handling of data is governed by their own privacy policy.

3. Data Storage

All user preferences (such as temperature units or theme settings) are stored locally on your device using standard iOS storage mechanisms. We do not maintain external servers for user data.

4. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

Our application does not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children under the age of 13.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us.
